<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">WORLD / CITY / DUNGEON CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Talk to people / Enter buildings / Check treasure chests / fast-forward the messages:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Turns the mini map on / off / Displays the entire message of a dialog box all at once:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Walk:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Displays status screen:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Rotate camera right or left:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 or L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Move camera up and down:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Puts a position indicator above the character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BATTLE CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Select command / Target character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Move camera right or left:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 or L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Confirm selection / fast-forwards messages / execute the action of the character in front:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Opens / Close action cancellation window of the back-up character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Executes action of the backup character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Fast-forwards messages / Opens or close action cancellation window of the character in front:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font><br>
        &nbsp;</td>
	 </tr>
	</table>
